Class HtmlUnitBrowserCompatCookieSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.http.impl.cookie.AbstractCookieSpec
      • org.apache.http.impl.cookie.CookieSpecBase
        • com.gargoylesoftware.htmlunit.httpclient.HtmlUnitBrowserCompatCookieSpec
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CookieSpec

    public class HtmlUnitBrowserCompatCookieSpec
extends CookieSpecBase
    Customized BrowserCompatSpec for HtmlUnit. Workaround for HttpClient bug 1006: quotes are wrongly removed in cookie's values.
    Author:
    Mike Bowler, Noboru Sinohara, David D. Kilzer, Marc Guillemot, Brad Clarke, Ahmed Ashour, Nicolas Belisle, Ronald Brill, John J Murdoch
